    dcterms:modified "2021-10-05T16:21:05+01:00" ;
    schema1:description "Hannah joined HMPPS in October 2019 to establish a new Reducing Reoffending Directorate, building on her experience of strategic policy making, cross-Government and local partnership working and programme delivery. Her directorate, renamed to Reducing Reoffending, Partnerships & Accommodation in 2020, works across Government, with the wider public and voluntary sector to reduce reoffending, primarily through improving accommodation, employment and substance misuse outcomes for prison leavers."@en ;
    schema1:name "Hannah Meyer"@en ;
